                            <comment id="14526617" author="githubbot" created="Mon, 4 May 2015 13:23:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user StephanEwen opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/645&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/645&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-1968&quot; title=&quot;Make Distributed Cache more robust&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-1968&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-1968&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;runtime&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Clean up and improve the distributed cache.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
